relatives

73
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:46,060
to call those reporters and ask them

74
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:48,950
to stop reporting on Xinjiang.

75
00:02:48,950 --> 00:02:51,480
But when threatening nicely didn’t work,

76
