83
00:03:05,849 --> 00:03:06,849
Don’t worry.

84
00:03:06,849 --> 00:03:10,730
It’s one of China’s top political reeducation
centers—

85
00:03:10,730 --> 00:03:13,560
along with the the Government Loves Everyone
Academy,

86
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:16,849
and the CCP Besties 4-Ever Institute.

