97
00:03:38,859 --> 00:03:40,260
He had contracted a case

98
00:03:40,260 --> 00:03:43,140
of what Chinese military doctors call,

99
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:45,159
“being a rights lawyer.”

100
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:47,290
A few hours after entering the hospital,

101
00:03:47,290 --> 00:03:49,099
the condition dramatically worsened

102
00:03:49,099 --> 00:03:52,650
