103
00:03:52,650 --> 00:03:55,170
Because of a liver problem.

104
00:03:55,170 --> 00:03:56,920
Yeah...

105
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:59,719
Some are calling rights lawyer Li Baiguang’s
death

106
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:02,430
